  "title": "Part-time Personal Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>URGENT</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Part-Time Personal Assistant</p>\n<p>- Flexible hours</p>\n<p>- Commitment of 3 days a week</p>\n<p>– $12/hr (Office)</p>\n<p>- $10/hr (WFH)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>• Maintain and provide secretarial support for the Consultants’ daily schedule, including forward planning of their workload and diary management</p>\n<p>• Assist in HR related matters</p>\n<p>• Perform any other ad-hoc tasks assigned</p>\n<p>• You will also be assisting with projects</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Minimum Local Diploma</p>\n<p>• Undergrads are welcomed</p>\n<p>• Age 21 and above</p>\n<p>• No experience needed (Training will be provided)</p>\n<p>• Able to work in fast-paced environment</p>\n<p>• Comfortable with multi-tasking</p>\n<p>• Be a team player</p>\n<p>• Possess good communication skills</p>\n<p>• Maintains confidentiality and possess sense of urgency</p>\n<p>• Highly organised, detail-oriented and responsible</p>\n<p>• Proficient in MS Office</p>\n<p>Opportunities of career progression to explore other roles.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>",
